Galileo Galilei. 1  Galileo published the first scientific paper based on observations made through a telescope in 1610. It was called The Starry Messenger. 2  In later years, the Catholic Church changed their views on Galileo and stated that they regretted how he was treated. 3  Galileo noticed that the planet Saturn wasn't round.
